This repo is to share working with the flash components in FDT. they all are include in the swc

You can see an example of this working on my blog http://hfug.net/?p=707

----------------------- using Flash Components in FDT -------------------------------
Flash CS 4
Create a new AS 3
drag a component to the library
in the publish settings make sure ".swc" is checked
publish movie

FDT
